# No environment variables are required.
#
# The waitlist now uses an EMBEDDED Klaviyo form (div class
# "klaviyo-form-W2JdnP") powered by the Klaviyo onsite script in
# src/layouts/Base.astro (company_id=SKABCW). Form fields, list
# assignment and double opt-in are all configured in Klaviyo.
#
# The old PUBLIC_KLAVIYO_COMPANY_ID / PUBLIC_KLAVIYO_LIST_ID custom
# Client-API approach was removed per the 18 May 2026 spec. Nothing
# to set here. `npm run dev` / `npm run build` need no .env.
